channel.title: InsanityX
channel.description:
Welcome to[b] InsanityX[/b], a brand new 317 server that brings to you anything you desire in a server.
[center][i]What is InsanityX? - Well InsanityX is a newly released server that has just been released to the public, it is a server that holds many adventures to everyone. We are an eco/pvm/pk server ( Alittle but of everything ) we promise you the economy will not be ruined because we pay very close attention to whats happening. We wanted to make an establish a rsps that will last for a really long time.[/i][/center]
[center][i]What does InsanityX include? - We include many stuff on our server, we have a little bit of customs for you customs lovers but on the same page we have the normal items as well, so we have mostly everything. We have all working skills, dung, summoning, etc. A nice pvm system along with a slayer system. You will never get bored of this server, there will always be things to do on here and I promise you that.[/i][/center]
[b]Website:[/b] http://insanityxx.enjin.com/home
Some of the features that InsanityX brings to you: ::Moneymaking which has giants that drop Rings (I) for money All skills working TokHaar-Kal with a unique way of achieving it All nex armours Great xp and drop rates to fit the server and economy Over 10+ on daily as a brand new server Dragon claws Dicing and flower game Dung with shop All bosses including some custom ones aswell Slayer task system Loyalty shop which include titles and customes Fullscreen adjustable Many shops All chaotics Custom party hats along with normal ones Barrows 100% working Unique assualt game minigame And so much more!
Pictures! Fun shop at rock crabs ( 1 point per kill of a rock crab ) [IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/jgqjav.png[/img]
Polypore dungeon [IMG]http://i61.tinypic.com/vphqhx.png[/img]
All these minigames to chose from [IMG]http://i62.tinypic.com/xaqmfk.png[/img]
Home with shops scattered around [IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/24m55zn.png[/img]
Pkp shop with some customs [IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/258b1iv.png[/img]
Bosses to chose from [IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/28t9sud.png[/img]
All skills working [IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/x52sjn.png[/img]
These wonderful capes [IMG]http://i57.tinypic.com/opralx.png[/img]
And so much more so just come check us out for your self! We are in need of staff but you need to prove to us you are staff worthy.
[b]Website:[/b] http://insanityxx.enjin.com/home
